<m:mi> a </m:mi>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-49">Velocity of the object under motion changes by an equal value in equal time interval. It implies that the velocity – time plot for constant acceleration should be a straight line. Here,
</para>
<para id="element-50">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>

<m:mfrac>
<m:mrow>
