</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-53">This is a linear equation in time “t” representing a straight line, where “a” is acceleration and is equal to the slope of the straight line and "u" is the intercept on velocity axis, representing velocity at t = 0. The plot of velocity with respect to time, therefore, is a straight line as shown in the figure here. 
</para>
<para id="element-54">
