</para>
<para id="element-77">We see that velocity does not change its sign. Thus, motion is unidirectional apart from being rectilinear. As such, distance is equal to displacement and is also 4 m. 
</para>
<para id="element-78">
Now, average velocity is given by :
</para>
<para id="element-79">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
