</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-80">
Similarly, average acceleration during the motion is :
</para>
<para id="element-81"><m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> v </m:mi>
<m:mn> avg </m:mn>
